    <item>
      <title>工党承诺银行中心恢复面对面服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/labour-pledges-banking-hubs-to-restore-face-to-face-services</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果工党赢得下个月的大选，它计划未来五年在英国各地建立 350 个新的银行“中心”，以扭转面对面服务的下滑趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/labour-pledges-banking-hubs-to-restore-face-to-face-services</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马约卡斯称，自拜登计划实施以来，过境人数大幅下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/border-crossings-fell-materially-since-biden-plan-mayorkas-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国土安全部部长亚历杭德罗·马约卡斯表示，自总统乔·拜登采取限制庇护申请的措施以来，穿越美墨边境的移民数量有所下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/border-crossings-fell-materially-since-biden-plan-mayorkas-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:10:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国左翼阵营发起集会呼吁团结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/france-s-left-bloc-starts-campaign-with-rally-calling-for-unity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国左翼政党领导人在周一晚间举行的首次竞选集会上呼吁团结，这些政党掩盖了根深蒂固的分歧，以组成联盟参加法国提前举行的立法选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/france-s-left-bloc-starts-campaign-with-rally-calling-for-unity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:06:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法庭评估泰国总理未来命运之际，他信即将被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/thaksin-set-for-indictment-as-court-weighs-thai-premier-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前领导人他信·西那瓦定于周二因诽谤王室而被正式起诉，与此同时，法庭正在考虑取消总理斯雷塔·塔维辛的任职资格——这两起备受关注的案件有可能让这个东南亚国家陷入政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/thaksin-set-for-indictment-as-court-weighs-thai-premier-s-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
